## This file is for LOCAL development only.
## Copy to `.env.local` (which should never be committed).
##
## IMPORTANT:
## - In a pure frontend (Vite) app, there is NO true secret.
## - Any variable that starts with VITE_ is public (shipped to the browser).
##
## Example of a "secret-like" value (DO NOT use in frontend in real life):
# DEMO_SERVER_ONLY_SECRET="dont-put-real-secrets-in-frontend"

